111
00:05:04,729 --> 00:05:06,360
Why would they do that if they were not in
cahoots

112
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,080
with the police or government, right?

113
00:05:08,080 --> 00:05:11,669
But again, just rumors, no solid proof.

114
00:05:11,669 --> 00:05:13,550
The Chinese Communist Party has an organization

115
00:05:13,550 --> 00:05:15,720
