116
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:18,270
Its members work with all sorts of groups—

117
00:05:18,270 --> 00:05:20,630
community leaders, politicians,

118
00:05:20,630 --> 00:05:23,680
organized crime, even religious authorities.

119
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:26,580
The goal of the United Front is to ensure
Chinese people

120
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:29,900
inside and outside China are loyal to the
Party.

121
00:05:29,900 --> 00:05:32,240
But this kind of influence is done subtly,

122
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:34,440
so it’s hard to find specific orders like

123
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:38,240
“I’ll pay you X dollars to attack this
group.”

124
